<i>Sick,</i>

484
01:13:42,017 --> 01:13:44,485
<i>(speaks native language)</i>

485
01:13:48,924 --> 01:13:54,487
<i>So the people came back to the woman
to ask her what to do,</i>

486
01:13:54,563 --> 01:13:57,464
