495
01:14:49,985 --> 01:14:52,317
<i>(distant howl)</i>

496
01:14:55,357 --> 01:14:57,348
<i>(howling)</i>

497
01:15:08,837 --> 01:15:10,828
<i>(howling continues)</i>

498
01:15:13,242 --> 01:15:15,574
<i>(speaks native language)</i>

499
01:15:20,783 --> 01:15:23,183
He knows, doesn't he?

500
01:15:24,186 --> 01:15:27,087
<i>He knows what they're saying,</i>

501
01:15:27,156 --> 01:15:32,093
The caribou are coming south
